- Why did you apply to play in the women's team? - I felt like a woman. - That is, I felt, you want to say? - Oh, yes. But what kind of sexism is this in the endings of words? What am I supposed to do now, tell me to relearn every time? So I studied, for example, Esperanto and perfectly mastered English - there are no feminine endings there. And in general, before the end of puberty, it is not known what will grow out of me there. And by the way, why are you interested in my gender?